=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rcp1665702759080.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rcp1665702759080.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rcp1665702759080.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rcp1665702759080\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Operation activated by the SAX parser when it encounters a start tag with one or more\n      <code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns</code> (namespace) specifications.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104rcp1665702759080_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__codeblock_qc4_rc3_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation STARTPREFIXMAPPING \n\n  params \n   string Prefix: in \n   string URI: in \n  endparams \n\nImplement your code here\n\nend; STARTPREFIXMAPPING</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__section_jf2_sc3_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1148873e56\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__ul_qmm_tc3_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__li_d48335e1_d48336e1_d48337e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Prefix</var>—namespace identifier. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__li_d48338e1_d48339e1_d48340e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">URI</var>—namespace identified by the\n          prefix. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__section_s13_5c3_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1148873e75\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__p_d136865e1_d136866e1_d136867e1\">When this operation is defined, it is called by\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSE</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSEFILE</span> when <code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns</code> is\n        encountered inside a start tag.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__p_d136868e1_d136869e1_d136870e1\">For example, given the following start tag:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104rcp1665702759080_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__codeblock_s3p_ld3_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;a:y xmlns=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/default\"&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__p_d136871e1_d136872e1_d136873e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTPREFIXMAPPING</span> is invoked three\n        times, with the following values:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Invocation Parameter Values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__1\">For XMl</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__2\">Value of Prefix</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__3\">Value of URI</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__4\">Comments</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/default\"</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"\"</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__3\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"http://www.mywebsite.com/default\"</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__4\">An <code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns</code>  specification that is not\n                followed by a colon and a prefix name sets a default namespace (that is, the URI)\n                for all tags up to the closing end tag. Any tag, up to the closing end tag, that\n                doesn’t have a prefix is considered to belong to the namespace indicated by this\n                URI. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns:a=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/a.html\"</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"a\"</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__3\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"http://www.mywebsite.com/a.html\"</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__4\">Any tag, up to the closing end tag, that starts with\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">a:</code> is considered to belong to the namespace indicated by this URI\n                  (<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"http://www.mywebsite.com/a.html\"</code>). </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns:a=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/b.html\"</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"b\"</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__3\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"http://www.mywebsite.com/b.html\"</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665702759080__table_d16313e1_d16314e1_d16315e1__entry__4\">Any tag, up to the closing end tag, that starts with\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">b:</code> is considered to belong to the namespace indicated by this URI\n                  (<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"http://www.mywebsite.com/b.html\"</code> ). </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kch1665703202145.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>PARSE</a><p>Parses a specified XML stream.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ttv1665703202809.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>PARSEFILE</a><p>Parses an XML document in the specified file.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xzo1665702759148.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ENDPREFIXMAPPING</a><p>Operation activated by the SAX parser for each namespace specification in a start tag, when the parser encounters the corresponding end tag.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531528\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531528\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "STARTPREFIXMAPPING Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Operation activated by the SAX parser when it encounters a start tag with one or more xmlns (namespace) specifications. Explain this code operation STARTPREFIXMAPPING params string Prefix: in string URI: in endparams Implement your code here end; STARTPREFIXMAPPING Copy Parameters Prefix —namespace identifier. URI —namespace identified by the prefix. Description When this operation is defined, it is called by PARSE and PARSEFILE when xmlns is encountered inside a start tag. For example, given the following start tag: Explain this code <a:y xmlns=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/default\"> Copy STARTPREFIXMAPPING is invoked three times, with the following values: Table 1. Invocation Parameter Values For XMl Value of Prefix Value of URI Comments xmlns=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/default\" \"\" \"http://www.mywebsite.com/default\" An xmlns specification that is not followed by a colon and a prefix name sets a default namespace (that is, the URI) for all tags up to the closing end tag. Any tag, up to the closing end tag, that doesn’t have a prefix is considered to belong to the namespace indicated by this URI. xmlns:a=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/a.html\" \"a\" \"http://www.mywebsite.com/a.html\" Any tag, up to the closing end tag, that starts with a: is considered to belong to the namespace indicated by this URI ( \"http://www.mywebsite.com/a.html\" ). xmlns:a=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/b.html\" \"b\" \"http://www.mywebsite.com/b.html\" Any tag, up to the closing end tag, that starts with b: is considered to belong to the namespace indicated by this URI ( \"http://www.mywebsite.com/b.html\" ). Related Links PARSE Parses a specified XML stream. PARSEFILE Parses an XML document in the specified file. ENDPREFIXMAPPING Operation activated by the SAX parser for each namespace specification in a start tag, when the parser encounters the corresponding end tag. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}